#---------------------------------------------------------------------- 
# GROUP POLICY

Q: Group policy to access everything in S3?
{
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "s3:*",
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}

Q: Group policy to everything in S3 with read only mode?
{
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:Get*",
        "s3:List*"
      ],
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}

Q: Allow everything on a specific bucket?
{
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "Stmt1361595623860",
      "Action": [
        "s3:*"
      ],
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::mucls.lynceantech.com"
      ]
    }
  ]
}

Q: Group ARN ?
arn:aws:s3:

#---------------------------------------------------------------------- 
# POLICIES

